Values from Source override destination, destination is returned (and modified!!)
Sample:
\>>> a = { 'first' : { 'rows' : { 'pass' : 'dog', 'number' : '1' } } }
\>>> b = { 'first' : { 'rows' : { 'fail' : 'cat', 'number' : '5' } } }
\>>> merge(b, a) == { 'first' : { 'rows' : { 'pass' : 'dog', 'fail' : 'cat', 'number' : '5' } } }
